ACTIVITY TYPES
• WALKING  (value  1 ): a subject was walking
• WALKING_UPSTAIRS  (value  2 ): a subject was walking up a staircase
• WALKING_DOWNSTAIRS  (value  3 ): a subject was walking down a staircase
• SITTING  (value  4 ): a subject was sitting
• STANDING  (value  5 ): a subject was standing
• LAYING  (value  6 ): a subject was laying down
